{"id":367202,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/10/bbc｜图辑：香港示威者在旺角同警察发生冲突/","date":"2014-10-17T22:56:10Z","modified":"2014-10-17T22:56:10Z","title":"BBC｜图辑：香港示威者在旺角同警察发生冲突","content":"<p>香港旺角星期五（10月17日）晚间再次发生示威者与警察之间的冲突，警察试图驱散在场聚集的示威者。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017175451_hk_976x549_ap.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017175451_hk_976x549_ap.jpg\" alt=\"141017175451_hk_976x549_ap\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017175451_hk_976x549_ap.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017175451_hk_976x549_ap-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n香港旺角星期五（10月17日）晚间再次发生警察与示威者之间的冲突，警察试图驱散在场聚集的示威者。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172852_hk_976x549_getty.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172852_hk_976x549_getty.jpg\" alt=\"141017172852_hk_976x549_getty\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172852_hk_976x549_getty.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172852_hk_976x549_getty-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n警方呼吁在场人士尽快离开现场， 并重申，如有违法行为，警方定会果断执法。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172744_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367214\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172744_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"141017172744_hk_976x549_reuters\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172744_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172744_hk_976x549_reuters-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n香港学联此前发表声明，批评香港政府星期五早上在旺角清场是早有预谋，而且一边表示对话，一边采取清场行动。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172631_hk_976x549_afp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367213\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172631_hk_976x549_afp.jpg\" alt=\"141017172631_hk_976x549_afp\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172631_hk_976x549_afp.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172631_hk_976x549_afp-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n最新的冲突发生在旺角弥敦道及亚皆老街交界地区，示威者一度冲破警方的防线并与警员对峙。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017171903_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367209\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017171903_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"141017171903_hk_976x549_reuters\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017171903_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017171903_hk_976x549_reuters-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n一些示威者似乎并不理会警方发出的警告。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172438_hk_976x549_ap.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367212\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172438_hk_976x549_ap.jpg\" alt=\"141017172438_hk_976x549_ap\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172438_hk_976x549_ap.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172438_hk_976x549_ap-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n混乱中，多人被警员带走，有人被警员按在地上制服。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172037_hk_976x549_afp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367210\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172037_hk_976x549_afp.jpg\" alt=\"141017172037_hk_976x549_afp\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172037_hk_976x549_afp.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172037_hk_976x549_afp-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n警方在举起黄旗及红旗警告后也多次喷射胡椒喷雾。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172202_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-367211\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172202_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"141017172202_hk_976x549_reuters\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172202_hk_976x549_reuters.jpg 976w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/141017172202_hk_976x549_reuters-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 976px) 100vw, 976px\" /></a><br />\n警方还拘押了Getty图片社摄影师Paula Bronstein。</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://a248.e.akamai.net/f/1/1/1/dci.download.akamai.com/35985/159415/1/c/\">中国数字时代亚马逊镜像</a> (墙内可直接点击)</p>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,8779],"tags":[10367,10943,11881,19948,25921,8712,23755]}